1. *Kriva* mi je linija. (The line is crooked.)
2. *Krive* su mi misli. (My thoughts are distorted.)
3. Njen *kriv* pogled me je uplašio. (Her crooked look scared me.)
4. Ona je *krivac* za sve što se dogodilo. (She is to blame for everything that happened.)
5. *Krivili* su ga za požar. (They blamed him for the fire.)
6. Prekršio je zakon pa će biti *kriv* za to. (He violated the law, so he will be guilty of that.)